[{"_path":"/blog/seo-guide-for-beginner","_dir":"blog","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"SEO 基礎入門：定義、價值與 SEO 與 SEM 的區別","description":"本篇「SEO 基礎入門」全面介紹什麼是搜尋引擎最佳化（SEO），並透過實例及圖表說明其對企業品牌與網站流量的影響。同時比較 SEO 與 SEM 的差異、探討自然搜尋優化的關鍵優勢與策略，讓新手也能輕鬆掌握如何在搜尋結果中脫穎而出。","image":"/img/seo-guide-for-beginner/google-search.png","date":"2025-03-04","tags":["seo","sem","seo入門","網站流量","網站優化"],"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"引言"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"引言"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在現今競爭激烈的網路時代，能否讓潛在顧客在搜尋時快速找到你的網站，往往左右企業的品牌曝光和獲利成長。SEO（Search Engine Optimization） 作為一種最具成本效益的行銷手段，越來越受到重視。本篇文章將從基礎概念出發，帶你了解 什麼是 SEO、它對企業品牌和流量的深遠影響，以及與 SEM（Search Engine Marketing）間的差異與優勢比較。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本文主要參考 Google 官方 SEO 入門指南的 SEO 教學，如有進一步研究需求，可參考相關資源以獲得更多技術細節。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"seo-定義"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SEO 定義"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"google-search","src":"/img/seo-guide-for-beginner/google-search.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"什麼是-seo"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"什麼是 SEO？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SEO（Search Engine Optimization）指的是通過優化網站的內容與技術結構，讓搜尋引擎（如 Google、Yahoo）更容易理解並收錄網站，使網站在自然搜尋結果中獲得更高的排名。和付費廣告不同，SEO 著重在提升「自然搜尋流量」，不需因點擊付費，長期而言能帶來更穩定且高質量的用戶。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"搜尋引擎的運作機制簡介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"搜尋引擎的運作機制簡介"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"爬蟲機制","src":"/img/seo-guide-for-beginner/%E7%88%AC%E8%9F%B2.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"爬蟲（Crawler）：搜尋引擎使用自動化程式抓取網頁內容，建立索引。 "}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"索引（Indexing）：搜集到的資料儲存在大型資料庫中，以備用戶查詢時快速比對。 "}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"排名（Ranking）：根據演算法對網頁進行排序，將認為最符合用戶需求、品質最佳的內容排在前面。\nSEO 的實質工作就是讓網站同時對「搜尋引擎」和「人」都友善，確保你的內容能被正確理解，並提供對用戶真的有幫助的資訊。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"為何自然搜尋優化如此重要"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"為何自然搜尋優化如此重要？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用者依賴搜尋引擎"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：據研究，超過 80% 的網路使用者會在搜尋引擎上查詢商品或資訊，並倾向在前幾頁找到答案。如果你的網站排名靠後，潛在客戶可能根本不會看到你。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"長期且穩定的流量"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：與付費廣告相比，SEO 的流量來源較為自然且持續，不會因為預算用完就立即消失。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"品牌可信度"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：用戶普遍認為「自然搜尋結果」更具有公信力，透過 SEO 讓網站排名靠前，可以在無形中提升品牌形象。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"seo-的重要性"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SEO 的重要性"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"如何透過-seo-提升品牌形象"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何透過 SEO 提升品牌形象"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"流量對比","src":"/img/seo-guide-for-beginner/%E6%B5%81%E9%87%8F%E5%B0%8D%E6%AF%94.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建立專業形象"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：網站出現在搜尋結果前段，往往讓人感覺更具信任度與權威性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"強化用戶體驗"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：SEO 涵蓋網站速度、行動裝置支援與內容價值等優化，帶給用戶更愉快的瀏覽體驗，自然強化品牌好感度。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"累積正面口碑"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：持續產出優質內容，可吸引更多人分享與引用，形成口碑循環，品牌影響力也水漲船高。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"對自然流量和轉換率的實際影響"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"對自然流量和轉換率的實際影響"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"轉換率","src":"/img/seo-guide-for-beginner/%E8%BD%89%E6%8F%9B%E7%8E%87.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高轉換率"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：搜尋行為通常代表用戶已有需求或興趣，若能在此時提供合適的資訊或產品，轉換成功機率高。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"低成本獲客"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：一旦關鍵字排名穩定，你就能透過搜尋引擎源源不絕地獲取免費流量，降低對付費廣告的依賴。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"數據回饋循環"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：透過工具（如 Google Analytics、Google Search Console）監控使用者行為和關鍵字，能進一步優化營銷策略，不斷提高網站的轉換率。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小提示：根據分享的實戰經驗，若能精準鎖定「長尾關鍵字」並提供對應優質內容，網站流量與轉換率都能呈現顯著成長。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"seo-與-sem-的區別"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SEO 與 SEM 的區別"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"自然搜尋優化seo-與-付費廣告sem-的基本差異"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自然搜尋優化（SEO） 與 付費廣告（SEM） 的基本差異"}]},{"type"